      "end": 47.52,
      "text": "Called The Secret Garden"
    },
    {
      "start": 47.52,
      "end": 49.7,
      "text": "Which this movie is based on"
    },
    {
      "start": 49.7,
      "end": 54.74,
      "text": "Yeah, she's well-known for 소공자 혹은 소공녀"
    },
    {
      "start": 54.74,
      "end": 57.72,
      "text": "이런 동화도 썼잖아요, 소설도 썼잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 57.72,
      "end": 59.44,
      "text": "A little prince and a little princess"
    },
    {
      "start": 59.44,
      "end": 60.22,
      "text": "이런 것들"
    },
    {
      "start": 60.22,
      "end": 63.5,
      "text": "워낙 유명한 작가입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 63.5,
      "end": 67.96,
      "text": "Yeah, very famous author of classic English children's literature"
    },
    {
      "start": 67.96,
      "end": 68.5,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 68.5,
      "end": 71.98,
      "text": "So I remember many of her works from when I was a kid"
    },
    {
      "start": 71.98,
      "end": 73.64,
      "text": "Including The Secret Garden"
    },
    {
      "start": 73.64,
      "end": 75.5,
      "text": "And it's been made into movies"
