    },
    {
      "start": 167.96,
      "end": 169.56,
      "text": "Does it matter if I care or not?"
    },
    {
      "start": 170.4,
      "end": 172.2,
      "text": "You are an odd duck, aren't you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 173.16,
      "end": 175.18,
      "text": "No, the first scene was in India"
    },
    {
      "start": 175.18,
      "end": 177.42,
      "text": "이 영화에서는요"
    },
    {
      "start": 177.42,
      "end": 180.64,
      "text": "처음 장면이 인도를 배경으로 나왔었어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 180.64,
      "end": 183.82,
      "text": "그러다가, what happened to her then?"
    },
    {
      "start": 183.82,
      "end": 186.06,
      "text": "So, she was orphaned"
    },
    {
      "start": 186.06,
      "end": 188.02,
